                <div class="content-block">
                    <h3 class="mb-4 text-secondary">Performance</h3>
                    <p>Lithium LiFePO4 batteries have an optimal energy density in both volume and weight and
                        have good specific energy, which means the battery can give the necessary power when
                        needed. It’s also worth mentioning that Lithium LiFePO4 batteries have excellent cycling
                        performance too.</p>
